Independent schools work to prepare their students for higher education, their chosen career and their place as citizens of the world.
As a sector of education capable of designing and implementing a tailored school curriculum, we find that contemporary languages remain popular and desirable in schools.
Nelson Mandela said: "If you speak to a man in a language he understands, you speak to his head.
If you speak to him in his tongue, you speak to his heart."
